OL,3,CEnergy bills to fall by #117 for
OL,4,Cmillions of British households from
OL,5,CApril
OL,7,FEnergy bills will fall by #117 for
OL,8,Fmillions of British households from
OL,9,FApril, Ofgem has said.
OL,11,FOfgem announced on Wednesday that the
OL,12,Fenergy price cap will fall by 7% from
OL,13,FApril 1 for a typical household in
OL,14,FEngland, Scotland and Wales.
OL,16,FThe regulator's price cap will drop
OL,17,Ffrom the current #1,758 to #1,641 - a
OL,18,Freduction of around #10 a month for
OL,19,Fthe average household using both
OL,20,Felectricity and gas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
