OL,3,CEnergy bills to fall by #117 for
OL,4,Cmillions of British households from
OL,5,CApril
OL,7,FChancellor Rachel Reeves said in
OL,8,FNovember that #150 would be cut from
OL,9,Fthe average household bill from April
OL,10,Fby scrapping the Energy Company
OL,11,FObligation (Eco) scheme introduced by
OL,12,Fthe Conservatives in government.
OL,14,FCustomers have been warned not to
OL,15,Fexpect a straight #150 discount on
OL,16,Ftheir bills, and that the cut will
OL,17,Fdepend on the size and type of
OL,18,Fhousehold and how much energy it uses.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
