OL,3,CEnergy bills to fall by #117 for
OL,4,Cmillions of British households from
OL,5,CApril
OL,7,F"We are cutting the cost of living,
OL,8,Fcutting the national debt and creating
OL,9,Fthe conditions for growth and
OL,10,Finvestment in every part of the
OL,11,Fcountry.
OL,13,F"It is the right economic plan to
OL,14,Fbuild a stronger and more secure
OL,15,Feconomy."
OL,17,FOn Ofgem's latest announcement, the
OL,18,Fregulator's director general of
OL,19,Fmarkets, Tim Jarvis, said: "Today's
OL,20,Fannouncement will be welcome news for
OL,21,Fmany households.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUwD@IO]{D@\OU
