OL,3,CEnergy bills to fall by #117 for
OL,4,Cmillions of British households from
OL,5,CApril
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,F"Wholesale energy prices have fallen
OL,13,Fin recent months, and we're investing
OL,14,Fin our network to safeguard the future
OL,15,Fenergy system.
OL,17,F"The main driver of today's reduction
OL,18,Fis the change to policy costs
OL,19,Fannounced by the Chancellor in the
OL,20,Fbudget.
OL,26,@tD@AOUyD@AOU
