OL,3,CEnergy bills to fall by #117 for
OL,4,Cmillions of British households from
OL,5,CApril
OL,7,F"Our focus at Ofgem remains on bearing
OL,8,Fdown on the costs within our control,
OL,9,Fand unlocking the investment needed to
OL,10,Fsupport the transition to a more
OL,11,Fstable energy system over the longer
OL,12,Fterm.
OL,14,F"We're also seeing encouraging signs
OL,15,Fof greater engagement and competition,
OL,16,Fwith switching increasing by almost
OL,17,F20% year on year."
